In October 2001 Offutt was charged with aggravated assault and attempted rape, the Daily News reported.

His former girlfriend told police he beat her and ripped off her clothes.

'Offutt tried to have intercourse with her,' a criminal complaint alleged. She 'had to fight Offutt to escape.'

The soldier's roommates woke up to the noise of the girl screaming, the complaint states. They found her 'naked and bleeding from the face.'

